webpackJsonp([0xc852188b4734],{1153:function(e,a){e.exports={data:{markdownRemark:{html:'<p>The current Ebola outbreak has seen the spread of a lot of misinformation and worry. This week’s Articulate Elearning Heroes Challenge was to create a quick Ebola awareness and information course. I love this idea because it illustrates how instructional designers can remain relevant by responding rapidly to widespread concern and misinformation with materials that set the record straight. I knew immediately I wanted that Keep Calm propaganda feel along with a dark, stark palette. The slender man also makes an appearance in the second slide. Don’t look directly at him!</p>\n<p><a href="http://knanthony.com/showcase/Ebola/story.html" title="Ebola Elearning Heroes Challenge">Check out the demo here</a>.</p>\n<figure>\n  \n  <span class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper" style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 385px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">\n    <span class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image" style="padding-bottom: 83.11688311688312%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;">\n      <img class="gatsby-resp-image-image" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;" alt="Ebola Course Screenshot" title="" src="/static/EbolaCourseScreenshot-fc8f504f6f0c3933bdf0c402c7063dbc-c8b9a.png" srcset="/static/EbolaCourseScreenshot-fc8f504f6f0c3933bdf0c402c7063dbc-76bbb.png 203w,\n/static/EbolaCourseScreenshot-fc8f504f6f0c3933bdf0c402c7063dbc-c8b9a.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 385px) 100vw, 385px">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n</figure>',frontmatter:{date:"October 13, 2014",path:"/blog/ebola-rapid-response",title:"Ebola Rapid Response",tags:["ebola","rapid response"],categories:["elearning","Elearning Heroes Challenge","Weekend Project"],featured:{childImageSharp:{sizes:{base64:"data:image/png;base64,",aspectRatio:1.768172888015717,src:"/static/logoColor-c92143fb3723fcd5f12c0d0502759756-81d39.png",srcSet:"/static/logoColor-c92143fb3723fcd5f12c0d0502759756-9a8d1.png 203w,\n/static/logoColor-c92143fb3723fcd5f12c0d0502759756-c53f9.png 405w,\n/static/logoColor-c92143fb3723fcd5f12c0d0502759756-81d39.png 810w,\n/static/logoColor-c92143fb3723fcd5f12c0d0502759756-e81a9.png 900w",sizes:"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px"}}}}}},pathContext:{}}}});
